body:
If `restore_bucketing` is `false`, then this will be printed for every address, possibly _many_ times. But it does not include the address itself. What about printing the address:

```suggestion
                LogPrint(BCLog::ADDRMAN, "Bucketing method was updated, re-bucketing addrman entry from disk for %s\n", info.ToString());
```

or print the generic message once:

```suggestion
                if (!printed) {
                    LogPrint(BCLog::ADDRMAN, "Bucketing method was updated, re-bucketing addrman entries from disk\n");
                    printed = true;
                }
```

